                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17320705-7-victim80 t17320705-7-viclabel44"></join>. On the 30th of June, in the Night, I lost about 150 Brass Patterns out of my Melting-House in <placeName id="t17320705-7-crimeloc45">King's-Head-Court, in Shoe-Lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17320705-7-crimeloc45" type="placeName" value="King's-Head-Court, in Shoe-Lane"></interp>
